high_descs: Turn around and move to the microwave on the opposite corner of the room.
Pick up the knife on the right side of the microwave.
Turn around and move to the bread on the island to the left.
Slice the bread on the counter.
Turn around and face the stove.
Open the first drawer to the right of the stove and place the knife inside.
Turn around and face the bread on the island.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Turn to the left and move to the microwave on the left.
Warm the bread inside the microwave.
Take the bread out and move to the fridge behind you.
Put the bread in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of warm toast in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and walk across to the opposite corner of the room to face the knife on the counter by the microwave.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and step forward to face the bread on the center table.
Cut the bread on the center table into slices.
Turn around and step forward to face the drawer to the right of the stove.
Place the knife in the drawer to the right of the stove.
Turn around to face the bread on the counter.
Pick up a slice of bread on the counter.
Turn around and step to the right to face the microwave.
Heat the bread in the microwave and remove it.
Turn around and cross the room to face the fridge.
Place the slice of bread in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To heat a slice of bread and place it in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around, then turn right towards the fridge, then turn left and walk to the microwave.
Pick up knife to the right of the microwave.
Turn left and walk to the loaf of bread on the center counter.
Cut the bread into slices.
Holding the knife, turn around and walk to the set of drawers to the left of the dishwasher.
Open the top drawer and place knife in to it.
Close the drawer and walk back to the sliced bread on the center counter.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Turn to your left and walk to the microwave.
Place the bread slice inside the microwave, then turn on microwave for four seconds, and then remove bread slice and close door.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Open fridge door and place bread slice on top shelf, then close fridge door.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved piece of bread in the fridge.
